{"tid":1634311,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"繼大山婆斷頸 支瑜腳仔軟","createTime":"2019-10-07T07:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T16:24:48.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cb3c9c108b4ca3a6573864b7b4da31fa477700c9","tid":1634311,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4422/4422661.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4422%2F4422661.jpg&h=009b1c44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE參加6日《SBS SUPER CONCERT》，一連帶來《FEEL SPECIAL》、《FANCY》和《YES or YES》三首歌曲，連日行程累積的疲憊，加上不停歇又有難度的編舞看得出疲憊。其中子瑜在表演最後一首歌時，一開場的擺手動作就不如以往有力，即使如此仍是維持專業笑容。<br />\n<br />\nTWICE出道4年來行程滿檔，除了年節休假外都是滿滿的行程，每年幾乎在南韓樂壇就回歸2到3次，同時還會準備日本新專輯和音樂節目表演，即使如此仍每次登場都展現樂觀開朗樣貌，每次表演也是竭盡全力。<br />\n<br />\n因此子瑜腿軟後倒的影片曝光後，粉絲都直呼真的很心疼，「這埸看近拍就知道第三首子瑜是靠意志力在撐&hellip;她的腳力道一開始就較沒有力氣了」、「去年到現在的幾首歌，舞蹈都很累，一起連著跳真的硬撐，加上打歌期本來就累，真的要多休息和保養身體，加油」。"},{"pid":"40403121e142d372a054bd03e7979e287990ba26","tid":1634311,"uid":165368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:34:07.000Z","msg":"ching點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dafef706dddb1219073543df6c22ff93d8bbe8e","tid":1634311,"uid":213969,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:35:55.000Z","msg":"做愛縱欲太多<br />\n梗係無力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8400d5982be963b10faf3af11e4df85a8d8051","tid":1634311,"uid":37146,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:50:25.000Z","msg":"有震蛋姐<br />\n跳完拎返出黎就冇事啦"},{"pid":"46f50e604c2361ec6ed404ab74a8d7b193ef60e8","tid":1634311,"uid":34241,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:17:53.000Z","msg":"sor9 唔小心開著左隻強力震強 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c166b926fe9fc165e169547cb35746